{"timestamp": "2025-12-05 16:33:21.589309", "event": "llm_end", "text": "Submission accepted.\n\nSummary of submission:\n- is_anomaly: true\n- localized faulty devices: dns_server, server_access_router, load_balancer\n- root cause names submitted: dns_record_error, http_acl_block\n\nIf you want, I can now:\n- Draft concrete remediation steps (DNS zone changes, server_access_router ACL/bridge fixes, removing/repurposing load_balancer.eth1) prioritized by risk and impact.\n- Run the follow-up inspections listed in the report (DNS zone dump, server_access_router config/iptables, FRR OSPF details, tcpdump traces) to produce specific commands and configs to remediate.", "generation_info": {"finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 3522, "output_tokens": 133, "total_tokens": 3655, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 2944}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 0}}}
